(z_n)_{n=1}^\infty
\sum_{n=1}^\infty {|z_n|^2}
\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{|z_n|}{n}
z_n=x_n+iy_n
x_n,y_n \in \mathbb{R}
n \geq 1
|z_n|^2=x_n^2 +y_n^2
n \geq 1
\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{|z_n|}{n}
\frac{|z_n|}{n}=\frac{\sqrt{x_n^2+y_n^2}}{n} \leq \frac{x_n^2 +y_n^2}{n}\leq x_n^2 +y_n^2
(\sum |z_n|/n)^2\leq (\sum |z_n|^2)(\sum 1/n^2)
N
N
\infty
